## Method
- Last {{ window }} runs per (model, adapter) pair, half-life decay {{ half_life }} days
- Per-run mean is tier-weighted: easy=1, medium=2, hard=3, very_hard=4
- Model-level score = highest-scoring adapter for that model (adapter is part of the test config)
- Implicit partial-credit gradient applied when only some required checks fail (capped at the "partial" weight)
